It’s been a bloody long journey to get where we are today, all starting back in early 2017 from when we first bought land up in Bucketty with dreams of farming hops and creating an off grid brewery, to importing junk equipment from China, to the council crushing our dreams. All the way until now, where we’re open in Brookvale. It’s been a ride! Show Less
